Downloads list of sessions.

Source: R/list_sessions.R
list_sessions.Rd

Downloads list of sessions.

list_sessions(vol_id = 1, vb = FALSE)

Arguments

vol_id

Target volume ID. Defaults to 1.
vb

A boolean value.

Value

List of sessions.

Examples

list_sessions()
